---
import DefaultLayout from "../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro";
---

<DefaultLayout>
  <section
    class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed uppercase"
  >
    <!-- SHIPPING -->
    <h2 class="mb-6 opacity-60">Shipping</h2>

    <p class="mb-6">
      All orders are dispatched from the United States and include tracking upon
      dispatch.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-10">United States — 2–5 working days</p>

    <!-- RETURNS -->
    <h2 class="mb-6 opacity-60">Returns</h2>

    <p class="mb-6">
      Returns are accepted within 14 days of delivery for refund only. Exchanges
      are not available.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      Items must be returned in original condition with all tags attached.
      Returns that do not meet these conditions may be refused.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      To initiate a return, contact <span class="lowercase"
        >support@malyxia.xyz</span
      > with your order number.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-10">
      Refunds are processed within 3–5 working days after inspection. Shipping
      fees are non-refundable unless the item is faulty.
    </p>

    <!-- THANK YOU -->
    <h2 class="mb-6 opacity-60">Thanks</h2>

    <p class="mb-6">
      Big thanks to everyone who contributed to this first chapter of MALYXIA —
      even when things didn’t go as planned, your support kept the project
      moving forward. This is still early, and we’re building it step by step.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-10 opacity-70">
      Special thanks to Axel Rodriguez, Alex Fortaneli, and Patrick.
    </p>

    <!-- FOOT LINKS -->
    <div class="mt-12 border-t pt-6 flex justify-between text-xs opacity-70">
      <a href="/privacy-policy" class="hover:opacity-100">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/" class="hover:opacity-100">MALYXIA</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>
